& \frac{(a-b)^3+(b-c)^3+(c-a)^3}{(a-b)(b-c)(c-a)} \\\\
& =3 \frac{(a-b)(b-c)(c-a)}{(a-b)(b-c)(c-a)}=3
\end{aligned}
